# --- Go build artifacts ---
# The Windows binary we ship; never check in builds.
artifact-review
artifact-review.exe
*.exe
*.test
*.out
dist/
bin/

# Go workspace files
go.work
go.work.sum

# --- Editor / OS noise ---
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# --- Case data and analyst artifacts ---
# Real DFIR case folders MUST NOT be committed. These can contain PII,
# IOCs, customer data, or material under legal hold.
#
# testdata/case/ DOES get versioned -- its fixtures (WS-EXEC-002,
# WS-FIN-014) are synthetic and required by the test suite. Use a
# DIFFERENT path for real cases (e.g. C:\Cases\<id>\) so they never
# land inside the repo by accident.
/cases/
/output/
*.csv
!testdata/**/*.csv
*.evtx
*.dat
*.hive
!testdata/**/*.dat
Empty_Artifacts.txt

# --- Preprocessor runtime junk ---
# The PS1 emits a run-zimmerman.log per host; never commit those.
run-zimmerman.log
*.log

# --- Third-party tool installers / runtimes ---
# Analysts often drop these next to the source while bootstrapping a VM.
windowsdesktop-runtime-*.exe
ZimmermanTools/
hayabusa/
hayabusa-*.zip

# --- Marks / per-user UI state ---
# marks.json lives in the case folder, but stray copies sometimes appear.
marks.json

# --- Misc ---
*.tar.gz
*.zip
